# Only the raw workspace scratch is ignored: it contains a NESTED git repo (the runner's
# baseline + the agent's work) that cannot live inside the parent repo, and its content is
# exported as plain text into rep-*/sut-authored/ anyway. The per-replicate EVIDENCE — the
# runner-side ACP transcript, meta.json, container-inspect.json, and the exported sut-authored
# trail — IS committed: the JSONL's artifact_dir pointers must resolve in a fresh checkout
# (per-replicate records are part of the benchmark contract, 40-benchmark).
records/smoke-out/rep-*/workspace/
